    "title": "Junior Investment Banker at BSE Global Group",
    "description": "BSE Global Group invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Investment Banker at our Mysuru location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout BSE Global Group:\nBSE Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mysuru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with BSE Global Group!",
